at the end

1. *Brige* su uglavnom izgrađene od drveta. (Bridges are usually built of wood.)

2. *Brigu* o svojoj bezbednosti ne smemo da zanemarimo. (We must not neglect our safety.)

3. Njegov otac imao je *brigu* o njegovom obrazovanju. (His father had concern for his education.)

4. *Briga* o deci je najvažnija. (Taking care of children is the most important.)

5. Vlada je pokazala *brigu* o ljudima u najtežim uslovima. (The government showed concern for people in the most difficult conditions.)